    "title": "Local Transfer API",
    "description": "The Local Transfer API enables seamless transactions for transferring funds between accounts within the same network. It streamlines the process of initiating and processing local transfers while ensuring data integrity and security. This API provides essential features for managing requests, responses, and various transfer parameters, along with robust error handling and logging capabilities.",
